title: Rockaway Beach, Wisconsin
text: Rockaway Beach is an <a href="Unincorporated%20area">unincorporated community</a> in the town of <a href="Stockbridge%20%28town%29%2C%20Wisconsin">Stockbridge</a>, <a href="Calumet%20County%2C%20Wisconsin">Calumet County</a>, <a href="Wisconsin">Wisconsin</a>, United States.
